### 9. PUT - Atualizar uma negociação
PUT http://localhost:5026/api/Negotiation/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expirationDate": "2026-01-31T23:59:59Z",
  "grossValue": 1500.00,
  "netValue": 1350.00,
  "discountValue": 150.00
}

###

### 10. DELETE - Deletar uma negociação
DELETE http://localhost:5026/api/Negotiation/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Valores do enum NegotiationItemType:
### 0 = Service
### 1 = Package
### 2 = Product

